Package: ggkegg
Type: Package
Title: KEGG pathway visualization by ggplot2
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person("Noriaki", "Sato", email = "nori@hgc.jp", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: This package aims to import, parse, and analyze KEGG pathway data. The package supports visualizing KEGG  information using ggplot2 and ggraph through a grammer of graphics.
